      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): advice to local authorities on prioritising waste collections
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A guide to help waste collectors prioritise their collection services during the coronavirus pandemic. This includes managing household waste recycling centres.</p>

  </div>
</div>

